<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CSS Varibles</title>
    <style>

        :root{
         --color: blue; 
        --seccolor: rgb(92, 197, 243);
        --defpad: 30px;
        }
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .nav {
            background-color: var(--color);
        }
        ul{
            display: flex;
        }
        
        ul li{
            list-style: none;
            padding: var(--defpad);
            border: 2px solid var(--seccolor);
        }
        
        ul li:first-child{
             --color: rgb(186, 12, 12); 
            background-color: var(--color);
        }

        .box {
            background-color: var(--seccolor);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="nav">
        <ul>
            <li>Home</li>
            <li>About</li>
            <li>Contact</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
        Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ea, iste laborum impedit sint corporis fuga soluta
        aperiam eos possimus non dolorem libero aspernatur recusandae quas aliquam nesciunt velit assumenda sunt quae
        earum numquam quo doloribus ipsam ut. Voluptatum reiciendis modi pariatur excepturi, dolore sint, hic sunt
        voluptatem nam id suscipit!
    </div>
</body>

</html>
